1. 注册表保存
GET
/api/registry/snapshot/save

响应：
返回的JSON结构：
成功：
{
    "code": 0,
    "message": "All registry backups completed successfully!",
    "status": "success",
    "backupDir": "C:\\backups\\Backup_20251018_195418",
    "timestamp": 1697654321000
}
部分失败：
{
    "code": -1,
    "message": "Some registry backups failed. Please check permissions or registry paths.",
    "status": "partial_failure",
    "backupDir": "C:\\backups\\Backup_20251018_195418",
    "timestamp": 1697654321000
}
完全失败：
{
    "code": 1,
    "message": "Registry backup failed to start. Unable to create backup directory!",
    "status": "failed",
    "backupDir": "",
    "timestamp": 1697654321000
}
异常：
{
    "code": -2,
    "error": "Failed to execute registry backup: [exception message]",
    "status": "exception"
}

